      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rangi / ſeptin zittas\nGohwis uſkahpe pehz ſchahm /\nto tahs Uppes / ar nejauku Gib-\ni / un leefahn Meeſahn / un\neestahjahs pee tahm zittahm\nGohwin/ Uppes Mallâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs Gohwis / kaſ tik\njauki iſlubkojahs / un no Mee-\nhm leefas bija/ eerihja tahs ſep-\na Gohwis / kam krahnis Gib-\nis bija / un treknas / tad at-\nohdahs Waraiis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz aiſmigge wiꞥſch at-\nt / un ſapnoja obtrkahrt / un\nugi/ ſeptin Wahrpas auge us\neenu Steebru/ breedufchas un\nchenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rangi/ ſeptin teewas un\nAuſtrixa nodeggufchas Wahṛ-\ns raddahs pehz tahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs teewas Wahrpas\nihje tahs ſeptin breedufchas un\nnas Wahrpas/tad atmohtdahs\naraüſ/ un redſi/ tas bija Sap-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke Rihtâ/ tad\na tas behdigs ſawâ Garrâ / un\nhtija/ un aiztnaja wiſſus Egip-\nn-Sihlneekus/un wiſſusGud-\ns / kas tur bija / un Waraiis\nze teem ſawus Sapnus/ bet ne\ncens bija / kas tohs Waraiim\nſtahſtitu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad runnaja tas Dſeh-\nma-Dewejo Wirneeks us Wa-\niu/ un ſazzija : Es atminnohs\nhodeen mannas Rodſeedſibas;\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad Waraiis hij apdu\nmojeeß prett fatweem Kalpeem/ un\nlikke mann ta Aumeiſtera Naun\nma Zeetuma/ mann/ un to Mat-\nfes-Zeppejo Wirneeku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un mums bija weenâ Na-\nti Sapnis / ikweenam ſawahd-\nSapnis/ ſawadi iſtahſtains.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur bija pee mum-\nweens Febrēiskis Jauneklis / t-\nAumeiſtera Kalps / un mehs pa-\nfazzijam tam tohs / un wiꞥſch ig-\nstahſtija mums ſawus Sapnus/\nikweenam iſtahſtija tas to peh-\nfawu Sapnoschanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta patt / ka tas mum-\nirr iſtahſtijis / irr tas notizzis,\nmann irr wiꞥſch atkat manna-\nWeeta eezeblis / un wiꞥſu ir-\nwiꞥſch pakahrıs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſuhtija Waraiis/ un\naizinaja Jahſepu / un tee likke ta-\nahtri no Bedres iſeet/ un wiꞥſch-\napzirpahs / un apwilke zittas\nDrehbes/ un nahze pee Waraiis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſazzija Waraiis uhe\nJahſepu : Es eſmu Sapni redſe-\njis/ un ne weens irr/ kas to iſtah-\nſta / bet es eſmu no tewini dsir-\ndejts ſakam/ kad tu weenu Sap-\nni dsirdi / to tu warrus iſtah-\nſtih.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahſeps atbiſdeja Wa-\nraiun / un ſazzija: tas ne ſtahw-\npee man/ Deews huuddinahs Wa-\nraiim wiſſu Labbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Waraiis ſazzija uhe\nJahſepu : Redſ/ es ſtahweju\nSapni Uppes Mallâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un redſi / tur uſkahpe no\n"
    }
